code: @Override public void run(String... args) throws Exception {     this.userRepository.deleteAll().     User user = saveUser().     System.out.println(this.userRepository.findById(user.getId())). }

private User saveUser() {     User user = new User().     user.setId(UUID.randomUUID().toString()).     user.setFirstName("Alice").     user.setLastName("Smith").     return this.userRepository.save(user). }
